[normal] has made it clear that there is unlikely to be any additional funding for 
[normal]local 
[normal]transport beyond the formula grant and LGF funding. 
[normal]5.2[bold] 
[normal]LEP 
[normal]representatives have
[normal] 
[normal]worked closely with the LTB to agree
[normal] 
[normal]the current priority 
[normal]major schemes 
[normal]and 
[normal]funding 
[normal]allocations and this commitment has been agreed. However the reality is that 
[normal]current funding levels for major schemes are not sufficient to help de
[normal]liver on the priority schemes and although we are hopeful, there is a lack of clarity that 
[normal]the levels of funding necessary 
[normal]will be secured through the Growth Deal
