[normal]6.2[bold] 
[normal]The 
[normal]devolution of funds
[normal] is welcome and over a longer period
[normal], but ideally 
[normal]it should be for local
[normal] LEP area
[normal]s
[normal] to decide the best 
[normal]organsiation
[normal]/ model for delivery
